                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000001fe45ece-152e-44cc-9c12-6b3f8b1e7879" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{{m}_{{o}_{1}}}{\sqrt{1-{0.8}^{2}}}=\frac{{m}_{{o}_{2}}}{\sqrt{1-{0.6}^{2}}}⇒{m}_{{o}_{1}}=\frac{3}{4}{m}_{{o}_{2}}\ ;\ \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000011fe45ece-152e-44cc-9c12-6b3f8b1e7879"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000001fe45ece-152e-44cc-9c12-6b3f8b1e7879 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000011fe45ece-152e-44cc-9c12-6b3f8b1e7879 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000dcf98d58-d90f-410e-a909-790915f5893c" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({m}_{{o}_{1}}&lt;{m}_{{o}_{2}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001dcf98d58-d90f-410e-a909-790915f5893c">e‡j, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({m}_{{o}_{1}}={m}_{o}∴{m}_{o}=\frac{3}{4}{m}_{{o}_{2}}\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000dcf98d58-d90f-410e-a909-790915f5893c {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001dcf98d58-d90f-410e-a909-790915f5893c {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000b15d9924-f2e1-4ec6-b87e-d8b4f8634c22" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001b15d9924-f2e1-4ec6-b87e-d8b4f8634c22">msN‡l&#169;i c~‡e&#169; †gvU kw&#179; = wgwjZ e&#175;‘i †gvU kw&#179;</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000b15d9924-f2e1-4ec6-b87e-d8b4f8634c22 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001b15d9924-f2e1-4ec6-b87