gvU †&#255;&#206;dj </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=2\times 2=4\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001fc41b44b-26d2-4415-ad4a-231b6c18986b"> </span><span class="pt-000002fc41b44b-26d2-4415-ad4a-231b6c18986b">eM&#169; GKK</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000fc41b44b-26d2-4415-ad4a-231b6c18986b {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001fc41b44b-26d2-4415-ad4a-231b6c18986b {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002fc41b44b-26d2-4415-ad4a-231b6c18986b {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000451e0ba9-2d30-420c-9092-292389c9d9c7" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001451e0ba9-2d30-420c-9092-292389c9d9c7"><img src="#" style="width: 1.241117in;height: 0.6727537in;" alt="Picture 1" /></span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000451e0ba9-2d30-420c-9092-292389c9d9c7 {}span.pt-000001451e0ba9-2d30-420c-9092-292389c9d9c7 {font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000884d066e-18a3-42cf-a37c-b5659a908127" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000884d066e-18a3-42cf-a37c-b5659a908127 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000eb3a6ce0-8447-45e9-ab6e-365fc54b3998" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001eb3a6ce0-8447-45e9-ab6e-365fc54b3998">weK&#237;: </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\int_{-2}^{0} \left(-x\right)dx+\int_{0}^{2} xdx\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000eb3a6ce0-8447-45e9-ab6e-365fc54b3998 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001eb3a6ce0-