                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000005cc301ef-9692-4409-9d54-691f741431a2" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000015cc301ef-9692-4409-9d54-691f741431a2"><img src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 1.111111in;height: 0.9009011in;" alt="Picture 1" /></span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000005cc301ef-9692-4409-9d54-691f741431a2 {}span.pt-0000015cc301ef-9692-4409-9d54-691f741431a2 {font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000917693f7-a8ff-417e-aeed-b5554670be8a" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{AC}{2P}=\frac{BC}{5P}=\frac{AB}{3P}∴BC=\frac{5}{3}AB\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001917693f7-a8ff-417e-aeed-b5554670be8a"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000917693f7-a8ff-417e-aeed-b5554670be8a {}span.pt-000001917693f7-a8ff-417e-aeed-b5554670be8a {font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000b9e678cf-82c5-4983-acc9-8ffe02d0fb59" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001b9e678cf-82c5-4983-acc9-8ffe02d0fb59">Abyiƒcfv‡e, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(B{C}^{{'}}=\frac{6}{3}AB\ ;C{C}^{{'}}=B{C}^{{'}}-BC=\frac{1}{3}AB\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001b9e678cf-82c5-4983-acc9-8ffe02d0fb59"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000b9e678cf-82c5-4983-acc9-8ffe02d0fb59 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001b9e678cf-82c5-4983-acc9-8ffe02d0fb59 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000cc997a4e-45ae-4634-aa04-a32be799588a" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001cc997a4e-45ae-4634-aa04-a32be79958